{"tid":2269297,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府就修訂打擊洗錢及恐怖分子資金籌集條例諮詢公眾","createTime":"2020-11-03T11:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T13:17:10.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e418203d1252b9c681b31f88a840c357761a4685","tid":2269297,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:37:42.000Z","msg":"政府就修訂《打擊洗錢及恐怖分子資金籌集條例》展開諮詢，建議透過引入虛擬資產服務提供者發牌制度；貴金屬及寶石交易商註冊制度，以及雜項技術修訂，加強規管打擊洗錢及恐怖分子資金籌集。<br />\n<br />\n諮詢為期3個月，直至明年1月底止。<br />\n<br />\n政府表示，立法建議目的是按財務行動特別組織公布的最新國際標準，完善香港監管制度。香港自1991年起成為組織成員。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人說，有關建議對香港履行相關責任，以及維持香港作為可靠及具競爭力投資及營商地方的公信力非常重要。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558178-20201103.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558178-20201103.htm&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo6jakGblTMbnvy6EODhsvCk%3D&h=9a084dee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558178-20201103.htm&h=7c2a8199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558178-20201103.htm</a>"},{"pid":"520dbc13a18de88ccdea532a67a4aed3b2add085","tid":2269297,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e895c80bb46dbd1ea388e9b0a2f2e68fcd0af8","tid":2269297,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"520dbc13a18de88ccdea532a67a4aed3b2add085","tid":2269297,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyT